The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for improving the solving methods for Answer-set programming (ASP), which is a subfield of non-monotonic reasoning and logic programming. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories as they are related to artificial intelligence and machine learning. The paper also involves the design and development of efficient ASP systems, which falls under cs.PL (programming languages). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of classification methods and features to select the best solver, which is related to cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) and cs.SE (software engineering).
